      • sendMultiplePackages

        @Loggable
public void sendMultiplePackages(java.util.List<ee.ria.dhx.types.OutgoingDhxPackage> outgoingPackages)
        Description copied from interface: AsyncDhxPackageService
        Send package. Package is sent to recipient defined in outgoingPackage. Method is asynchronous, therefore not returning anything, but after package is sent, callback method will be called. Every package is sent to recipient defined in it. If package sending gets exception, then send document result with fault in it is created, sending will be continued anyway. Callback is called for every package separately.
        Specified by:
        sendMultiplePackages in interface AsyncDhxPackageService
        Parameters:
        outgoingPackages - - package to send
